Author : Thomas Vervisch

Mooc.soluceapp.com is an application that aims to facilitate the teaching of economics. It makes it easier for students to be graded in person or remotely. It offers graded and non-graded activities as well as a system for creating worksheets for the revision of exams.

All that remains to be done is to:

Core of the application: The core of the application is generally to be completed.

- Find new activities to note such as inventory management. 
- Improve the ergonomics of the site by creating a drop-down list for the choice of scenarios. 
- Improve the security of the site through the creation of tokens. 
- Create a system for transferring classes in administration from one year to the next.

